Presidential spokesperson Khusela Diko is facing a disciplinary hearing for alleged failure to disclose all her financial interests. SIU report to decide fate for Khusela Diko, Bandile Masuku and Loyiso Masuku:  While that investigation is ongoing – the SIU says it hasn’t yet found any evidence pointing to Diko’s involvement in the awarding of two contracts by the health department to Royal Bhaca, her husband’s company.